OL,3,CHow can you avoid falling victim to a
OL,4,Cphone or online scam?
OL,6,FIf someone claiming to be from
OL,7,FMicrosoft calls you about a virus on
OL,8,Fyour computer, or if you receive a job
OL,9,Foffer that seems too good to be true,
OL,10,Fhang up and do your research.
OL,12,FContact the company directly to verify
OL,13,Fwhether it's a scam.
OL,15,FAsk family or friends
OL,17,FIf you are suspicious about a call or
OL,18,Ftext, ask a family member or friend to
OL,19,Fhelp verify whether the company is
OL,20,Flegitimate or a scam.
